Backend (Node.js with Express):

Set up Express server
Implement MongoDB connection using Mongoose
Create API routes
Implement authentication (JWT)
Set up Stripe and Lemon Squeezy integrations

Frontend (React):

Set up Create React App or Next.js
Implement routing with React Router
Create a landing page
Set up authentication UI (login/register forms)
Implement protected routes
Create checkout components for Stripe and Lemon Squeezy

SEO and DNS:

Implement SEO meta tags
Set up DNS records
